name: Cozy House (Shi-City #0001)
description: Cozy House is 1st on our list of Shi City NFT.  Tokenized Town which you can collect Buildings and Structures using NFT to create your own Collectibles that we'll call it as Shi City.  Shi City has also citizens that we call as ShiTizens. You can acquire them as how many as you can.  To keep its scarcity, value of NFTs from my company will raised every month depending on the rarity and type (For those collectibles that weren't bought). But if you successfully bought it, you can resell it as much as you want!
